        "subject": "LU-17049 doc: add enable_*_gid.4 man pages",
        "message": "LU-17049 doc: add enable_*_gid.4 man pages\n\nAdd mdt.enable_pin_gid.4, mdt.enable_chprojid_gid.4, and\nllite.enable_setstripe_gid.4 man pages, and link them into\nthe appropriate sections of the related lfs-pcc-pin.1,\nlfs-project.1, lfs-setstripe.1, lfs-quota.1, etc. pages.\n\nUpdated modified man pages to quiet many checkpatch-man warnings.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nFixes: 84100d7f7d (\"LU-10499 pcc: tunable GID to pin/unpin files\")\nFixes: 8fad70c087 (\"LU-12826 mdt: limit root to change project state by default\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@thelustrecollective.com>\nChange-Id: Iad289d560d3048e98ee32ffd691852aed73ebbe5\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/64709\nReviewed-by: Sohei Koyama <skoyama@ddn.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Sebastien Buisson <sbuisson@ddn.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
